      <title>乌克兰无人机袭击后俄罗斯弹药库起火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/russian-ammunition-depot-ablaze-after-ukrainian-drone-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰称其无人机袭击了俄罗斯沃罗涅日地区的一个弹药库，乌克兰总统泽连斯基再次敦促盟友允许使用远程武器打击军事目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/russian-ammunition-depot-ablaze-after-ukrainian-drone-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 13:41:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利高级官员称今年仍有信心实现 1% 的增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/italy-still-confident-of-1-growth-this-year-top-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利政府有信心今年经济增长率将达到 1%，这是总理乔治亚·梅洛尼履行对欧盟减债承诺的关键指标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/italy-still-confident-of-1-growth-this-year-top-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 12:56:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和哈里斯将宾夕法尼亚州视为 2024 年竞选主战场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/trump-harris-eye-pennsylvania-as-main-battleground-of-2024-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宾夕法尼亚州正逐渐成为白宫竞选的主战场，卡马拉·哈里斯和唐纳德·特朗普越来越多地将注意力和资源集中在这个关键州。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/trump-harris-eye-pennsylvania-as-main-battleground-of-2024-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价下跌削弱了特朗普对哈里斯的通胀攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/falling-pump-prices-dampen-trump-s-inflation-attacks-on-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普试图通过攻击卡马拉·哈里斯的能源记录来激怒对通胀感到厌倦的消费者，而汽油价格的稳步下跌为美国副总统卡马拉·哈里斯竞选美国最高职位提供了顺风。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/falling-pump-prices-dampen-trump-s-inflation-attacks-on-harris</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基与梅洛尼在科莫湖会面，展望乌克兰重建</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/zelenskiy-and-meloni-meet-at-lake-como-look-ahead-to-ukraine-s-rebuilding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管乌克兰与俄罗斯的停火协议仍未达成，但乌克兰总统泽连斯基和意大利领导人乔治亚·梅洛尼同意努力争取明年在意大利举行一次会议，重点讨论乌克兰战后重建问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/zelenskiy-and-meloni-meet-at-lake-como-look-ahead-to-ukraine-s-rebuilding</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 11:38:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰进军俄罗斯令盟友印象深刻，但又感到担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/ukraine-s-push-into-russia-leaves-allies-impressed-but-worried</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰大胆进攻俄罗斯库尔斯克地区，并迅速取得初步成功，给基辅的盟友留下了深刻印象，颠覆了人们对战争陷入僵局的看法，也暴露了弗拉基米尔·普京不惜一切代价保卫领土的誓言的空洞性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/ukraine-s-push-into-russia-leaves-allies-impressed-but-worried</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅洛尼称政府稳定不受部长丑闻影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/italian-government-unaffected-by-minister-resignation-meloni-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利文化部长詹纳罗·桑朱利亚诺周五辞职后，意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼反驳了有关其政府内部不稳定的暗示。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/italian-government-unaffected-by-minister-resignation-meloni-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 09:55:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞尔维亚实施道路封锁后科索沃关闭两处边境口岸</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/kosovo-closes-two-border-sites-following-serbian-road-blockades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，塞尔维亚团体拦截了部分持有科索沃证件的旅客，随后科索沃关闭了与塞尔维亚的两个边境口岸，导致该地区的紧张局势升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/kosovo-closes-two-border-sites-following-serbian-road-blockades</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 09:42:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国新总理将推进现金刺激计划以振兴经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/new-thai-pm-to-push-ahead-with-cash-stimulus-to-revive-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国新任总理巴东丹·西那瓦誓言要推进备受争议的 140 亿美元现金刺激计划，其内阁已敲定蓝图，旨在帮助东南亚第二大经济体摆脱长期低增长和家庭债务困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/new-thai-pm-to-push-ahead-with-cash-stimulus-to-revive-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 05:45:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默和拜登将于下周会晤讨论战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/why-is-uk-prime-minister-keir-starmer-visiting-ireland</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默和美国总统乔·拜登将于下周在华盛顿举行会议，讨论包括以色列与哈马斯战争在内的问题，因为两国在处理这场持续 11 个月的冲突时出现了分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/why-is-uk-prime-minister-keir-starmer-visiting-ireland</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
